            <title>[CASSANDRA-10947] Remained files in the hints folder</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-10947</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;I&apos;ve found a lot of (over 2 million) .crc32 files in the hints folder:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;[data]# du --max-depth=1
7800    ./saved_caches
271420  ./data
175776  ./commitlog
9219368 ./hints
9674368 .
[data]# ls -1 hints/ | wc -l
2250624
[data]# du hints/
9220336 hints/
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
                <environment>&lt;p&gt;Cassandra 3.0.0, CentOS 7.2 x64&lt;/p&gt;</environment>
